- content: string — universal across all providers. Gemini wraps in object but content is serialized
- isError: Anthropic has is_error field, others don't. Worth capturing generically for error-aware tool handling

## Why 'ToolResult' not 'ToolResponse'
- Aligns with existing metadata key ('result'), Anthropic API ('tool_result'), codebase conventions
- Avoids collision with InferenceResponse, HttpResponse terminology

